results.name: Local maxima of A265894 just before its descents: a(n) = A265894(A265899(n) - 1).
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..2016
program: A099563(n) = { my(i=2,dig=0); until(0==n, dig = n % i; n = (n - dig)/i; i++); return(dig); };
results.author: _Antti Karttunen_, Dec 24 2015
